            description: "Cybereye Option. User adds +2 to their Perception, Lip Reading, and Conceal/Reveal Object Skills for Checks which include sight. Requires two Cybereyes and must be paired. Multiple installations of this option provide user no additional benefit. See p.360.",
        ),
