            description: "Cybereye Option. Reduces penalties imposed by darkness and other intangible obscurement, like smoke, fog, etc. to 0. User can distinguish hot meat from cold metal but cannot see through anything that could provide cover. Requires two Cybereyes, must be paired, and takes 2 Option Slots per Cybereye. See p.360.",
